<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Nope. I read Ender&apos;s Game and went right to this one. I actually liked being able to see the same story from another perspective, see what the others <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Nope. I read Ender's Game and went right to this one. I actually liked being able to see the same story from another perspective, see what the others were doing while Ender was losing his mind at command school. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
