<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/321515-i-absolutely-loved-ender-s-game-and-only">I absolutely loved Ender&#39;s Game, and only liked the following two books in the trilogy. Would you compare this story to the intensity of Ender&#39;s Game or one of the other books?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_321515'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F9532.Ender_s_Shadow">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/321515-i-absolutely-loved-ender-s-game-and-only">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/321515-i-absolutely-loved-ender-s-game-and-only">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

